# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:4
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_35f375de:

    # "I'm tired, and I feel awful. I just don't have it in me to chase everyone down right now."
    "我累了，感觉糟透了。现在的我已经没有心思去追上大家了。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:5
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_4afbae1d:

    # "Flynn's back off to Echo, and it looks like Leo went after TJ, but I can't imagine the lynx wants all of us crowding around him right now."
    "Flynn已经回镇子去了，而Leo看样子是去追TJ了，我猜那只山猫这会儿也不喜欢被一堆人围着。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:6
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_ff3ef48d:

    # "I sigh, rubbing my face before I sit down in the lawn chair next to Carl."
    "我叹了口气，揉了揉脸，坐到Carl旁边的折椅上。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:8
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_9d6e111c:

    # "He looks over at me, slowly lowering what's definitely a joint from his mouth."
    "他看着我，慢慢把他嘴里绝对是大麻烟一样的东西放了下来。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:9
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_eb9ecf91:

    # m "\"What? I don't mind.\""
    m "\"怎么了？我又不介意。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:10
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_68fd6b4f:

    # "I make a \"go on\" gesture with my paw."
    "我用爪子做了一个\"继续啊\" 的手势。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:11
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_97f771b6:

    # "Carl shakes his head though, pushing the disheveled tube back into his front pocket."
    "Carl摇了摇头，把那支蓬乱的烟卷塞回了前面的口袋。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:12
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_a2c48387:

    # c "\"Nah, I always kinda feel like a dick when the other guy isn't into it.\""
    c "\"不用了，总感觉要是别人不喜欢，我还继续的话，那我还真挺混蛋的。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:13
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_d569cbbd:

    # m "\"Want me to leave?\""
    m "\"那，要我离开吗？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:14
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_e05f1ab7:

    # "He shakes his head with a quick flick of his horns."
    "他迅速地摇了摇头，长角也因此微微晃动。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:15
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_aeb895ae:

    # c "\"No man. I just do it when there's nothing else to do.\""
    c "\"不用，伙计，我只会在很无聊的时候才吸几口。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:16
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_d1171c7d:

    # m "\"Ah.\""
    m "\"喔。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:17
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_0d0490e0:

    # "There's a moment of silence and I feel a little pressure to break it since I'm the one who interrupted his bake session."
    "有片刻我们陷入了沉默，我想找点话题，但由于我刚打断了他的愉快时光，所以有点犹豫。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:18
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_a4475848:

    # m "\"I actually tried it a few years ago.\""
    m "\"其实我几年前尝试过一次。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:20
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_9d749842:

    # "Carl looks surprised."
    "Carl看上去很惊讶。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:21
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_ecc4be53:

    # c "\"Oh really? How was it?\""
    c "\"哦，真的吗? 感觉如何啊？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:22
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_8619f2c6:

    # "I shrug."
    "我耸耸肩。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:23
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_be077fbd:

    # m "\"Pretty bad. Was in a muffin, I think.\""
    m "\"很烂，放在松饼里那种。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:25
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_f40b08f8:

    # "Carl makes a face at that."
    "Carl听完吐了吐舌头。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:26
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_fa185cee:

    # c "\"Edibles.\""
    c "\"用来吃的那种啊。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:27
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_5d8df134:

    # m "\"Yeah, well, I ended up eating one, didn't feel anything for a while. Next thing I know I'm face down on the floor and everyone's freaking out.\""
    m "\"嗯，没错，我只吃了一个，一开始还没有什么感觉。 反应过来的时候自己已经面朝下倒在地板上，把大家都被吓坏了。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:28
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_f6457192:

    # c "\"Shit, that sucks.\""
    c "\"这也太惨了吧。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:29
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_5dd25630:

    # m "\"It was kinda funny, but I don't think I'll ever try it again.\""
    m "\"其实还有点意思，但我绝对不会再试这玩意了。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:30
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_b28e8e36:

    # "Carl pulls the joint back out of his pocket and holds it up."
    "Carl从口袋里拿出大麻烟卷，在我面前举了举。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:31
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_dc85b68a:

    # c "\"That's why you should use one of these. It's easier on the brain.\""
    c "\"你应该试试这个，对大脑没那么刺激。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:32
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_352135b3:

    # m "\"Yeah, well, I guess I just don't like the idea of putting smoke in my lungs.\""
    m "\"好啊，呃，感觉我还是不喜欢把烟吸到肺里。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:34
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_cec9f0c1:

    # "Carl puts the joint back in his pocket."
    "Carl又把大麻烟放回了口袋。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:35
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_65f7d5c5:

    # c "\"I get that.\""
    c "\"了解了。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:36
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_b2bc173f:

    # "Again, there's a few seconds of silence and I try to think of something to say, but Carl beats me to it."
    "我们的交谈又停滞了几秒，我刚想找点话题，Carl却先开了口。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:39
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_de9ffa41:

    # c "\"Crazy shit, huh?\""
    c "\"很疯狂，不是吗？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:40
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_e9b0587a:

    # "I assume he's talking about what just happened."
    "我猜他说的是刚才发生的事。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:41
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_ca35a6a0:

    # m "\"Yeah, crazy.\""
    m "\"是啊，太疯狂了。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:42
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_51121ffa:

    # c "\"But you know how he is. He's regretting everything right now.\""
    c "\"但是你知道他是个怎样的人，他现在应该在懊悔他的所作所为吧。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:43
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_9c08cd60:

    # m "\"Well, I guess I'd rather he just wouldn't say it in the first place.\""
    m "\"比起这个，我更希望他从没说过那些话。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:44
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_270151bb:

    # m "\"What he said to TJ, man...He picks on him a lot, but that was crossing the line.\""
    m "\"他对 TJ 说的那些话，真的...虽然他平时就喜欢在他身上找乐子，但这次真的过头了。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:45
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_2d0f805a:

    # "Carl scratches behind one of his horns, then rubs his nose."
    "Carl用手在后面挠挠他的长角，接着蹭了下鼻子。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:46
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_187dff40:

    # c "\"Well yeah, I guess I never understood that, either. Making fun of TJ is like...making fun of a cloud.\""
    c "\"是啊，我也一直不能理解这一点。在TJ身上找乐子，他得有多无聊啊。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:47
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_218dd5d6:

    # c "\"But Flynn doesn't mean it, usually. He likes TJ.\""
    c "\"但或许Flynn真的只是闹着玩，平时他还挺喜欢TJ的。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:48
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_f5b60c76:

    # "I've noticed during the trip that Carl's been pretty defensive of Flynn, even though he's the butt of most of the lizard's jokes."
    "在旅途中我注意到Carl处处维护着Flynn，尽管他通常都沦为了蜥蜴的笑柄。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:49
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_305af9a9:

    # "I'd seen Flynn trip Carl up and put him in several headlocks since I got here."
    "自我来到这里后，看到过Flynn故意绊倒Carl，锁过几次喉什么的。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:50
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_7688eb54:

    # "You'd think getting older would change that, but I swear they roughhouse even more than they did before."
    "你可能会觉得随着年龄增长，这些行为都会逐渐减少，但我发誓他们现在比以前更加粗暴。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:51
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_1ce63498:

    # m "\"So you and him still seem pretty close. You guys hang out a lot?\""
    m "\"看上去你和他关系还不错啊，你们经常一起玩吗？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:52
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_e9a77382:

    # c "\"Yeah, a bit, mostly because there isn't much else to do. He's got a friend in Payton that he hangs out with sometimes, too.\""
    c "\"嗯，算是吧，主要是平时真的很无聊啊。他在沛顿市有个朋友，他们偶尔会出去玩。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:53
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_234fe411:

    # m "\"So what do you guys do?\""
    m "\"那，你们平时都玩些什么？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:54
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_42262411:

    # "I know Flynn isn't into video games at all, and Carl probably doesn't care to go clubbing every other night."
    "我知道Flynn对电子游戏完全没兴趣，Carl可能也不愿意隔天就去次夜店。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:55
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_1939486d:

    # "He shrugs."
    "他耸了耸肩。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:56
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_0e6e9a3a:

    # c "\"Sometimes we go fishing, maybe just drive around Payton.\""
    c "\"有时我们会去钓鱼，或者就单纯开车去沛顿兜兜风。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:57
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_2acd8435:

    # c "\"Mostly I'm just hangin' out at home, though.\""
    c "\"不过我大多数时候还是待在家。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:58
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_705d68a8:

    # m "\"Playing video games?\""
    m "\"打电玩？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:59
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_f560a9cc:

    # c "\"Playing video games, watching movies, cybering with a chatbot—the usual.\""
    c "\"平时都是玩游戏，看电影，和聊天机器人聊骚什么的。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:60
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_b91092c0:

    # "I grin."
    "我笑了出来。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:61
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_a57b2520:

    # m "\"That's sad, I would have cybered with you if I'd known you didn't have anyone.\""
    m "\"那也太惨了吧，要是我知道没人陪你的话就和你在网上聊聊骚了。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:63
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_7340ce0a:

    # c "\"I dunno man, that thing compiles all the fetishes of the people it's talked to. It's gotten my sexuality all kinds of fucked up.\""
    c "\"唉伙计，这个东西还收集了所有和它交谈过的人的癖好。 把我的性癖都搞得一团糟。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:64
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_73453da0:

    # m "\"Oh yeah?\""
    m "\"真的？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:65
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_087883c6:

    # c "\"Yeah, seems like no matter what I say to her she's tied up in some warehouse, blindfolded with a few missing limbs.\""
    c "\"是啊，看起来不管我怎么试着和她交流，她都像是被关在某个货仓里，绑起来蒙着眼睛，肢体残缺。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:66
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_a0f997ed:

    # m "\"You underestimate my abilities.\""
    m "\"那你可真是低估了我的接受能力。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:67
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_288a50ff:

    # c "\"Oh, and a gender swap that comes out of nowhere halfway through.\""
    c "\"哦，还有中途不知从哪冒出来的性转剧情。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:68
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_12023c7d:

    # m "\"Well, while you're not sexing up a robot, you doing anything else?\""
    m "\"好吧，除了勾引那个机器人之外，你平时还做什么？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:69
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_289165cb:

    # "He chuckles."
    "他噗嗤一声笑了出来。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:70
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_557c310f:

    # c "\"I can't exactly get around myself anymore.\""
    c "\"实际上我没法再到处乱跑了。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:71
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_970f3f41:

    # m "\"So I guess your parents decided against getting you a new car?\""
    m "\"所以，你父母不打算给你买辆新车了？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:72
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_1ee33683:

    # c "\"Yeah...Oh! Look at this.\""
    c "\"嗯...噢！看看这个。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:73
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_e41aecfa:

    # "He leans over and pulls out his phone. I can't help but notice it's a top model brand, probably around $700."
    "他弯下腰掏出手机，我不禁注意到这可是名牌，高端型号，大概要700美刀。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:74
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_fe352408:

    # "But he's not showing me the phone. Instead he presses at the screen a few times and swipes through some pictures."
    "但他拿出来可不是炫耀手机的。他对着屏幕点了点，划过几张图片。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:75
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_ed48ccd5:

    # "I swear I see an image of Flynn with his pants down mooning the camera."
    "我发誓我看到了一张Flynn脱下裤子光屁股对着摄像头的照片。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:76
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_85e96ca4:

    # "Carl swipes over it pretty quick, though, and now I'm looking at the image of a brand-new sedan—"
    "不过，Carl很快就划过了这张图，现在我看到的是一辆崭新轿车——"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:77
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_75650fa2:

    # "—except the front is neatly folded up around the pole of a stop sign."
    "——只不过车头两边翘了起来，中间是一个杆子——那是一个停止指示牌"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:78
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_48f1dd9e:

    # "I recognize the sign; I'd actually seen it right outside the convenience store, still bent at a ridiculous angle."
    "我认出了那块牌子；我还真在便利店外面看到过它，在我看到时依然以一个离谱的角度弯折着。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:79
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_cd22333d:

    # "Guess the town didn't care enough to get it fixed."
    "大概镇上的人都不怎么在意这牌子有没有被修好吧。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:80
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_40df7195:

    # "The pole itself is almost embedded into the middle of the hood."
    "停止指示牌的杆子几乎已经嵌入到了引擎盖中。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:81
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_49c3a117:

    # m "\"Holy shit.\""
    m "\"我的天啊。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:82
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_38421c67:

    # "Carl chuckles and pinches the screen, zooming in."
    "Carl咯咯笑着，两指捏住屏幕，将照片放大。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:83
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_22d83893:

    # c "\"Yeah. Dropped my phone and when I came back up this freakin' pole was right in front of me.\""
    c "\"是啊。当时我手机掉了，等我再看路面的时候，这该死的杆子就已经在我面前了。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:84
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_de755be0:

    # m "\"Really, Carl? Why were you on your phone?\""
    m "\"真的吗，Carl？你为什么会一边开车一边打电话？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:85
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_49c2b9c4:

    # c "\"I dunno. When I get to the town I don't really think anyone's gonna be on the road.\""
    c "\"我没想到啊， 我以为进了镇子后路上就没人了。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:86
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_1c1a8c3c:

    # "I sigh, then notice a big, round, spot on the right side of the windshield, spiderwebbed and smashed white."
    "我叹了口气，然后注意到在挡风玻璃的右侧有着一大块圆形，蛛网状白色裂痕的区域。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:87
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_02912309:

    # m "\"Whoah, is that—\""
    m "\"天啊，那是——\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:88
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_4a56110d:

    # c "\"Yup!\""
    c "\"没错！\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:89
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_1afd0539:

    # "Carl knocks on his head for effect, the hollow sound that it emits seeming rather appropriate."
    "Carl敲了敲他的头作示范，它所发出的空洞的声音听上去相当合适。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:90
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_b76a1dc6:

    # m "\"You rely on that too much...and you really need to start wearing your seatbelt.\""
    m "\"你不能靠这个...你真的应该开始系安全带了。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:91
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_4f9e5124:

    # "He shrugs and puts the phone back in his pocket before leaning back in the chair and closing his eyes."
    "他耸耸肩，把手机放回口袋，然后靠着椅背，闭上了眼。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:92
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_aa5789bc:

    # c "\"What's the point?\""
    c "\"为什么？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:93
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_84beda0a:

    # m "\"Uh, to not die?\""
    m "\"唔，为了不挂掉？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:94
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_05bd4fd6:

    # c "\"Happens to everyone sooner or later. Why not get out early if you can?\""
    c "\"人迟早都会死的，既然如此，早点不是更好？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:95
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_ce878b0d:

    # "He keeps his voice light under the heavy statement."
    "他语气很轻松，说出的话却如此令人压抑。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:96
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_394f21f4:

    # "I have no idea what to say to that, so I don't, but he breaks the silence again soon enough."
    "我一时语塞，不清楚该说些什么，但很快，他又开口了。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:97
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_ac730e89:

    # c "\"So how's PU, you see Chelsea at all?\""
    c "所以你在PU过得怎么样, 见到Chelsea了吗？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:98
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_0390bddd:

    # "Sometimes I forget Carl went to Pueblo with me. It was only one semester, but we had a lot of fun."
    "有时候我都会忘记Carl曾和我在Pueblo大学上过学。尽管只有一个学期，但那段时光我们相处得很愉快。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:99
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_fb63abaf:

    # m "\"It's alright, haven't seen Chelsea at all though.\""
    m "\"过得还行，不过我还没见过Chelsea呢。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:100
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_1f19a9a7:

    # c "\"It is a big school. Anyway, what's that project thing you're doing?\""
    c "\"这可是个很大的学校。对了，你在做的那个课题是关于什么的？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:101
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_5f5f034d:

    # m "\"Just a news packet about Echo, really. Kinda about how it's falling apart.\""
    m "\"只是一个关于回音镇的系列报道，调查回音镇是如何衰落的。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:102
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_d145bd36:

    # c "\"Huh.\""
    c "\"噢。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:103
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_36c22690:

    # "I've told him this already, but Carl never remembers much."
    "这我之前已经和他讲过了，但他总是记不了多少。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:104
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_3b7f7a23:

    # m "\"Might center it around the whole 'body in the mine' thing that happened way back.\""
    m "\"可能会围绕着‘矿井藏尸’这则旧事件展开调查吧。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:105
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_f3830e54:

    # "Carl opens his eyes and looks at me."
    "Carl睁大眼睛，看着我。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:106
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_388684f2:

    # c "\"So do you need like, history stuff, like old books and records and stuff?\""
    c "\"那么你需要历史资料吗，比如旧书籍，录音带之类的？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:107
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_354b2d00:

    # m "\"Uh, yeah. If it relates.\""
    m "\"嗯，需要和事件有关的。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:108
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_cc4e7c31:

    # "Carl sits up straighter and grins."
    "Carl咧嘴一笑，坐得更直了。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:109
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_71172ae3:

    # c "\"Well, why didn't you say so! We've got a ton of stuff in the crawl space from way back when.\""
    c "\"那你为什么不早说！ 我们的地下储藏室里面就有一大堆那个时候的东西。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:110
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_beb34505:

    # m "\"Yeah? What kind of stuff?\""
    m "\"真的?都是些什么样的东西啊？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:111
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_08769ab5:

    # "Carl sets a hoof against one of the rocks circling the fire pit and starts rocking his chair back."
    "Carl把一只蹄子抵在篝火边的一块石头上，向后靠上椅背，晃动着椅子。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:112
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_13ba3054:

    # c "\"Well, whatever my family kept over the years. That one guy, um...\""
    c "\"嗯，是我家里人多年来存放的一堆东西。嗯，那个人叫…\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:113
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_ca4e0347:

    # "Carl snaps his fingers a few times."
    "Carl一边回忆，一边打着响指。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:114
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_db291537:

    # c "\"You know, the guy...founded this place, uh...\""
    c "\"你知道的，建设这个地方的那个人，叫什么来着...\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:115
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_8b3adc27:

    # m "\"James?\""
    m "\"James？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:116
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_24b1676b:

    # c "\"Yeah, sure. He's like, my great-great-great grandfather, or something. I think we still have some of that stuff from back in the day.\""
    c "\"对哦。 他好像是我的曾曾曾祖父什么的。 我想我们还留有他那个时代的东西。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:117
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_0b40b763:

    # c "\"My parents were thinking about setting up an Echo museum thing, but they never did.\""
    c "\"我的父母有想过建立一个回音镇博物馆之类的，但也仅止步于构思而已。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:118
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_2ac53029:

    # "This might actually be useful to me."
    "这没准真的会对我的调查有所帮助。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:119
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_c8acb1d9:

    # "All I had planned was to maybe look over some old newspapers or town records and be done with it."
    "我之前的计划就单单只是翻阅一些旧报纸和一些小镇里保存的资料，仅此而已。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:120
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_b08c9136:

    # "Actually seeing some old stuff up close could be pretty cool."
    "要是能近距离观察到一些旧物件还挺酷的。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:121
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_e2d2ab49:

    # m "\"That might be a good idea, actually.\""
    m "\"没准这还真是个不错的主意。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:122
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_65c01c4b:

    # "Carl grins."
    "Carl笑了笑。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:123
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_5e2c20e7:

    # c "\"Awesome. I always kinda wanted to look through that stuff, but the crawl space is damn creepy. You free tonight?\""
    c "\"太好了。我一直都想瞧瞧那些老式玩意，但是地下夹层那地方总让我毛骨悚然。你今晚有空吗？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:124
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_b847a7e3:

    # "For the first time Carl actually looks really excited."
    "这还是我回来后第一次见到Carl这么兴奋的样子。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:125
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_5761d19b:

    # c "\"Oh wait, nevermind. Flynn's taking me to a dentist appointment early in the morning. How about around 11 tomorrow?\""
    c "\"哦，等下，算了。Flynn明天一早就要带我去见牙医。明天11点左右如何？\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:126
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_ad10a89a:

    # "I smile."
    "我笑了笑。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:127
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_fcd77b2f:

    # m "\"Sounds like a plan.\""
    m "\"就这样吧。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:128
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_213e4d59:

    # c "\"Sweet! WHOAH!\""
    c "\"好极了！哇呼！\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:134
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_412e5d6d:

    # "Carl gives an excited kick off the rock and, as the chair's tipping back, the back legs practically snap under his weight."
    "Carl兴奋地一脚踢开了那块石头，椅子也随之向后倾斜，椅子后腿在他的重压之下咔嚓一声断了。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:135
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_2371f7e8:

    # "He's sent slamming down on his rear, the chair a crumpled mess under his ass."
    "他猛地摔了个底朝天，身下的椅子也被他压扁了。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:137
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_c1b4ebc0:

    # "I laugh and of course I feel bad, but Carl just gets up with a sheepish smile, looking down at the broken pile."
    "我一边同情他，一边忍不住笑出了声，而Carl带着困窘的笑容站了起来，然后低头看了看那堆破烂。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:140
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_49bf1fcb:

    # c "\"Welp, Leo's gonna be pissed.\""
    c "\"嗨，这下Leo可要发火了。\""

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:146
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_349767db:

    # "I'm driving down the road alongside the lake."
    "我沿着湖边的路开着车。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:147
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_178a1a28:

    # "Carl's sitting next to me."
    "Carl就坐在我身旁。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:148
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_9cfb4b27:

    # "He's in the chair that he broke."
    "坐在他之前弄坏的那张椅子上。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:149
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_2d6e0875:

    # "I keep telling him to wear his seatbelt, but he won't."
    "我一直要他把安全带系上，但他就是不听。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:150
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_b52004f2:

    # "I turn down a road I don't remember."
    "我拐进了一条陌生的路。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:151
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_ce7d8eef:

    # "It goes straight down towards the lake."
    "这条路直通湖边。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:152
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_a0be163e:

    # "For some reason I can't stop."
    "不知为何，我刹不住车。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:153
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_c48b782f:

    # "I brace myself for the impact, but I hardly feel anything."
    "我准备好迎接冲击，却什么都没有感觉到。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:154
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_4447945b:

    # "We just glide into the lake."
    "我们就这样滑入湖中。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:155
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_76aedc5e:

    # "I start trying to take off the seatbelt, but it's stuck."
    "我试着解开安全带，但却卡住了。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:156
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_00e95b94:

    # "I look over at Carl and he smiles before opening his door."
    "我看向Carl，他对我笑了笑，然后打开了门。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:157
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_668cb0c2:

    # "Water rushes in, and he starts to step out."
    "水涌了进来，而他向外走去。"

# game/Monday-Carl.rpy:158
translate Schinese sitwithcarl_3f992232:

    # "Soon the water is over my head, and it doesn't matter that I'm an otter."
    "很快，水就没过了我的头顶，这种情况下我作为一只水獭也无能为力了。"

